      "para_id": "Q001244.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) Me-silim , king of Kiš , builder of Ninĝirsu's temple , diplayed this ( mace ) for Ninĝirsu ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001244.7",
      "line_range": "7",
      "translation": "(7) ( At that time ) Lugal-šag-engur was the ruler of Lagaš ."
    }
